item.title: Kicking off 2023
item.description: I never do much on New Years Eve. I can't remember the last time I stayed up until Midnight. It's just not really a big deal with me. Yesterday, thanks to Natan rushing tickets, I did close out the year seeing the Metropolitan Opera's new production of Fedora which was very enjoyable. Woke up late today - around 5:00, went for my first run of the year and did the puzzle over coffee.
